-- Vestas Plans “Significant Change” to Organization Next Week
-- B y   W i l l   W a d e
-- 2012-01-03T17:49:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-03/vestas-plans-significant-change-to-organization-next-week.html
Vestas Wind Systems A/S (VWS) , the world’s
largest wind-turbine maker, plans to announce a “significant
change” to its corporate structure Jan. 12.  The company had expected to announce the change in
February, and is moving faster than anticipated, Aarhus,
Denmark-based Vestas said today during a conference call.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Will Wade at 
 wwade4@bloomberg.net  